data.description: Experience the comfortable lifestyle you deserve in this charming, well-maintained 5 Bedroom x 4 Bath two-story residence that backs to open space on a tranquil cul-de-sac within the highly desirable Willow Trace neighborhood & Cherry Creek School District. As you step inside, you'll be welcomed by a sun-filled and open-concept floorplan adorned by brand-new luxury vinyl hardwoods, vaulted ceilings, and warm-toned paint throughout; seamlessly connecting the living and dining areas. Preparing meals and enjoying gatherings is effortless in this renovated chef's kitchen that features newer Brazilian slab granite wrap-around countertops that treat guests to bar seating, a newer 4-piece matching stainless steel appliances set, ample cabinetry, and adjacent breakfast nook with quick access to the patio where you can entertain friends with weekend BBQ cookouts. Cap off the day unwinding in the spacious family room with a chic tile surround gas fireplace or enjoy movie nights in solitude with the blackout curtain drapes. An updated powder room rounds out the main level. Up the stairs, ultimate relaxation awaits in the wide-reaching primary suite w/ double door entry, walk-in closet, and private en suite 5-piece bath that's been remodeled with Brazilian slab granite countertops, dual sink vanity, and newer vinyl plank flooring. Three generously sized bedrooms, an updated full bath with Brazilian granite-topped vanity & newer tile flooring complete the upper level. The basement provides even more flex space with a guest bedroom (w/ egress window), custom-designed  3/4 bath, and laundry room. Outside, you'll find a fenced-in lawn that backs to open space and a new 10' x 30' concrete patio with an extended path that connects your front and back yards. Other notables: brand new roof & gutters (2023), newer HVAC (2020), newer hot water heater, and two storage sheds. Very low HOA. Walking distance to schools. Nearby Southlands Mall, shops & restaurants, parks, and walking trails.
